  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "This standard is an extension of [EIP-721](./eip-721.md). It proposes an additional role (`user`) which can be granted to addresses, and a time where the role is automatically revoked (`expires`). The `user` role represents permission to \"use\" the NFT, but not the ability to transfer it or set users.",
